<% content_for :banner do %>
  <%= render :partial => "moonwalk/investor_banner" %>
<% end %>
<div class="grid_12 alpha omega about_content">
  <div class="grid_12 alpha omega">
    <div id="media_player_main" class="video_box">

    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="media_videos" class="grid_12 alpha omega">
    <h2>Moonwalk Cardio Founder and Inventor Dennis Dubois</h2>
    <div class="grid_12 alpha omega multi_player video_box">
      <%= image_tag('media_thumbs/dennis.jpg') %>
      <div class="grid_9">
        <h3>Dennis pt-1 (Getting Started)</h3>
        <p>
Dennis is the Inventor and Founder of the Moonwalk Cardio Anti-Gravity System.  Dennis has struggled with working out for years due to his weight problems.  Dennis has spent countless hours designing, testing, and developing what is quickly becoming the Next Generation in Cardio Fitnes,  the CARDIO-SUIT.  This system has been able to help Dennis better understand all aspects of what it takes to achieve a comfortable workout with the massive weight removal, as well as alleviating the pain associated with weight problems on joints, and giving YOU the best most comfortable and positive workout imaginable.
        </p>
        <p>
          <%= link_to "Watch It", "", :id => "dennis1_clip", :rel => 'div.overlay' %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid_12 alpha omega multi_player video_box">
      <%= image_tag('media_thumbs/dennis2.jpg') %>
      <div class="grid_9">
        <h3>Dennis pt-2 (The 10 minute mark)</h3>
        <p>
          Dennis is just into the warm up period. Things are going good as he drops another 30 pounds on him.
        </p>
        <p>
          <%= link_to "Watch It", "", :id => "dennis2_clip", :rel => 'div.overlay' %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid_12 alpha omega multi_player video_box">
      <%= image_tag('media_thumbs/dennis3.jpg') %>
      <div class="grid_9">
        <h3>Dennis pt-3 (The 30 minute mark)</h3>
        <p>
          Part 3 of the series - Dennis has found a groove as he cruises along in his workout. Moving along at 3 mph with 200 pounds lifted from him. Hes able to workout comfortably.
        </p>
        <p>
          <%= link_to "Watch It", "", :id => "dennis3_clip", :rel => 'div.overlay' %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid_12 alpha omega multi_player video_box">
      <%= image_tag('media_thumbs/dennis4.jpg') %>
      <div class="grid_9">
        <h3>Dennis pt-4 (The 45 minute mark)</h3>
        <p>
          Part 4 of the series - 45 minutes into it and he still moving along strong. Feeling better than he has in a long time. The revolutionary <%= APPLICATION_NAME %> Machine has allowed Dennis to workout with ease. Removing the pressure and weight that would otherwise prevent him from doing such a wrokout. 
        </p>
        <p>
          <%= link_to "Watch It", "", :id => "dennis4_clip", :rel => 'div.overlay' %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="overlay">
    <div id="player">    
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'video_scripts' %>
</div>
